message: "People were in denial you know how could a safe community that supports its children have something like this going on?" said Soroptimist member Laura Powell. "It's truly stunning, in a very bad way but in fact it does exist."

data.description: KENNEWICK, Wash.-- The United Way and Soroptimist International of Pasco joined together to host an event called Stop Human Trafficking Community Conversation.
data.title: Local organizations host event to bring human trafficking awareness
